title: 宝塚記念の後に・世界の強豪へ！

text_block_list.text: Matikanetannhauser put on a wonderful race.
The bespectacled reporter watching quietly seemed to gain courage, thinking she should also do her best.
Meanwhile, Matikanetannhauser, while rejoicing in her victory, immediately proposes the next target race: the 'Japan Cup', where top contenders from around the world gather.
She says she's not confident she can win, but she wants to take on the challenge. With her... the days of charging toward the 'Japan Cup' begin!
